The paper deals with image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of sparse decomposition and total variation minimization suggests that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). The regularization terms used in the algorithm suggest that it may also fall under the category of statistical learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
